    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This *+1 striking returning trident* is made of an ancient black metal that glistens unnaturally and is cold to the touch. The prongs of this trident drip with metallic lake water. Strikes with the *Devil's Trident* trigger the weaknesses of any creature with a weakness to water.",
